nslation", :text=>"Lamech’s other wife, Zillah, gave birth to a son named Tubal-cain. He became an expert in forging tools of bronze and iron. Tubal-cain had a sister named Naamah."}, {:version=>"English Standard Version", :text=>"Zillah also bore Tubal-cain; he was the forger of all instruments of bronze and iron. The sister of Tubal-cain was Naamah."}, {:version=>"Berean Study Bible", :text=>"Zillah also gave birth to Tubal-cain, a forger of every implement of bronze and iron. And the sister of Tubal-cain was Naamah."}, {:version=>"New American Standard Bible ", :text=>"As for Zillah, she also gave birth to Tubal-cain, the forger of all implements of bronze and iron; and the sister of Tubal-cain was Naamah."}, {:version=>"New King James Version", :text=>"And as for Zillah, she also bore Tubal-Cain, an instructor of every craftsman in bronze and iron. And the sister of Tubal-Cain "}, {:version=>" Naamah.", :text=>"King James Bible"}, {:version=>"And Zillah, she also bare Tubalcain, an instructer of every artificer in brass and iron: and the sister of Tubalcain ", :text=>" Naamah."}, {:version=>"Christian Standard Bible", :text=>"Zillah bore Tubal-cain, who made all kinds of bronze and iron tools. Tubal-cain's sister was Naamah."}, {:version=>"Contemporary English Version", :text=>"Lamech and Zillah had a son named Tubal Cain who made tools out of bronze and iron. They also had a daughter, whose name was Naamah. "}, {:version=>"Good News Translation", :text=>"Zillah gave birth to Tubal Cain, who made all kinds of tools out of bronze and iron. The sister of Tubal Cain was Naamah. "}, {:version=>"Holman Christian Standard Bible", :text=>"Zillah bore Tubal-cain, who made all kinds of bronze and iron tools. Tubal-cain's sister was Naamah. "}, {:version=>"International Standard Version", :text=>"Zillah gave birth to Tubal-cain, who became a forger of bronze and iron work. Tubal-cain's sister was Naamah. "}, {:version=>"NET Bible", :text=>"Now Zillah also gave birth to Tubal-Cain, who heated metal and shaped all kinds of tools made of bronze and iron. The sister of Tubal-Cain was Naamah. "}, {:version=>"New Heart English Bible", :text=>"Zillah also gave birth to Tubal Cain, who heated metal and shaped instruments of bronze and iron. Tubal Cain's sister was Naamah."}, {:version=>"GOD'S WORD® Translation", :text=>"Zillah also had a son, Tubalcain, who made bronze and iron tools. Tubalcain's sister was Naamah."}, {:version=>"JPS Tanakh 1917", :text=>"And Zillah, she also bore Tubal-cain, the forger of every cutting instrument of brass and iron; and the sister of Tubal-cain was Naamah."}, {:version=>"New American Standard 1977 ", :text=>"As for Zillah, she also gave birth to Tubal-cain, the forger of all implements of bronze and iron; and the sister of Tubal-cain was Naamah."}, {:version=>"King James 2000 Bible", :text=>"And Zillah, she also bore Tubalcain, an instructor of every forger in bronze and iron: and the sister of Tubalcain was Naamah."}, {:version=>"American King James Version", :text=>"And Zillah, she also bore Tubalcain, an instructor of every artificer in brass and iron: and the sister of Tubalcain was Naamah."}, {:version=>"American Standard Version", :text=>"And Zillah, she also bare Tubal-cain, the forger of every cutting instrument of brass and iron: and the sister of Tubal-cain was Naamah."}, {:version=>"Brenton Septuagint Translation", :text=>"And Sella also bore Thobel; he was a smith, a manufacturer both of brass and iron; and the sister of Thobel was Noema."}, {:version=>"Douay-Rheims Bible", :text=>"Sella also brought forth Tubalcain, who was a hammerer and artificer in every work of brass and iron. And the sister of Tubalcain was Noema. "}, {:version=>"Darby Bible Translation", :text=>"And Zillah, she also bore Tubal-Cain, the forger of every kind of tool of brass and iron. And the sister of Tubal-Cain was Naamah."}, {:version=>"English Revised Version", :text=>"And Zillah, she also bare Tubal-cain, the forger o